\v 7 Nokuti pasina chikonzero vakandivanzira mumbure wavo \add mu\add*gomba; pasina chikonzero vakacherera mweya wangu\x + Map. 9.15. 140.5.\x*.
\v 8 Kuparadzwa ngakusvike kwaari akarivara\x + 1 VaTes. 5.3.\x*; uye mumbure wake waakavanza ngaumubate iye; ngaawire mauri pakuparadzwa\x + 1 VaTes. 5.3.\x*\x + Map. 7.15.\x*.
