\v 9 Asi mweya wangu uchafarira Jehovha; uchapembera muruponeso rwake\x + Map. 9.14. Ruk. 1.47.\x*.
\v 10 Mapfupa angu ese achati\x + Map. 51.8.\x*: Jehovha, ndiani wakaita semwi, munonunura murombo pane ane simba kumupfuura\x + Eki. 15.11.\x*, hongu murombo nemushaiwi pane anomupamba\x + Map. 86.1.\x*?
\p
\v 11 Zvapupu zvezvakaipa zvinosimuka; vanondibvunza zvandisingazivi\x + Map. 27.12.\x*.
\v 12 Vanonditsivira zvakaipa pachinzvimbo chezvakanaka; mune mariro\x + Map. 38.20. Jer. 18.20. Map. 109.4.\x* mumweya wangu.
\v 13 Asi kana ndiri ini, pakurwara kwavo chipfeko changu chaiva saga\x + Map. 69.10,11. Job. 30.25. 1 Madz. 20.31.\x*; ndakaninipisa mweya wangu nekutsanya, uye munyengetero wangu wakadzokera muchipfuva changu\x + Mat. 10.13. Ruk. 10.6. Map. 79.12.\x*.
\v 14 Ndakafamba sezvinonzi ishamwari uye sezvinonzi ihama kwandiri; ndakakotama\x + Map. 38.6.\x* kuchema seanochema mai\x + Map. 38.6.\x*.
\v 15 Asi pakugumburwa kwangu vakafara, vakaungana pamwe; vakarasiwa vakaungana kundirwisa, zvino ndaiva ndisingazivi; vakabvambura vakasamira\x + Job. 16.9.\x*.
\v 16 Sevakaipa vanodadira pamabiko\x + Job. 8.13.\x* vakandigedera mazino avo\x + Map. 37.12. Job. 16.9.\x*.
