\v 17 Ishe, muchatarisa kusvika rinhi? Dzosai mweya wangu pakuparadza kwavo, mudikanwi wangu padzishumba\x + Habh. 1.13.\x*.
\v 18 Ndichakuvongai paungano huru; ndichakurumbidzai pakati pevanhu vane simba\x + Map. 22.25.\x*.
