\v 25 Ngavarege kuti mumoyo wavo: Hekani, chishuvo chedu\x + 35.21. Map. 140.8.\x*; ngavarege kuti: Tamumedza\x + Marir. 2.16.\x*.
\v 26 Ngavanyadziswe, vazvidzwe pamwe chete, vanofarira padambudziko rangu\x + 35.4.\x*; ngavafukidzwe nekunyara nekuzvidzwa\x + Job. 8.22.\x*, ivo vanozvikudza pamusoro pangu\x + Job. 19.5.\x*.
