\v 27 Ngavadanidzire nemufaro, vafare, ivo vanoshuva kururama kwangu\x + VaRom. 12.15.\x*; hongu ngavati rinhi narinhi\x + Map. 40.16. 70.4.\x*: Ngaakudzwe Jehovha\x + Map. 34.3.\x*, iye anoshuva\x + Map. 149.4.\x* rugare rwemuranda wake\x + Map. 73.3. 2 Sam. 11.7.\x*.
\v 28 Zvino rurimi rwangu rwuchataura kururama kwenyu, zuva rese kurumbidzwa kwenyu\x + Map. 71.24. Map. 51.14. 71.8,15. Map. 37.30.\x*.